output: On day two, the planned activities are: visiting Quán Âm Diệu Vân Pagoda, Long Sơn Pagoda (Vạn Hoa), Chiang Kai-shek Memorial Hall, Vạn Thánh Sơn Hải Tạng Pagoda, Từ Hàng Memorial Hall, Jiufen Old Street, and Luohua Night Market, before returning to Quán Âm Diệu Vân Pagoda. Additional sightseeing points include Nam Sơn Phóng Sanh Pagoda, Hải Tạng Pagoda, and Từ Hàng Memorial Hall. Lunch will be at a vegetarian restaurant, and dinner will be self-catered at the Luohua Night Market.
